description                                     bootstrap class 
=====================================================================
(1) for label                                    form-label 
(2) for input type = text, password, date,      form-control 
datetime-local, time, month, email, number,
etc 
    textarea tag

(3) select-option                               form-select 
(4) input type = range                          form-range 
(5) input type = color                          form-control-color form-control
(6) input type = radio / checkbox               
    in parent div (vertically)                  form-check 
    in parent div (horizontally)                form-check-inline 
    in input type                               form-check-input 
    in input label                              form-check-label

(7) for input group 
    parent div                                  input-group 
    input type                                  form-control 
    label/ button                               input-group-text 

